'''polar coordinates''' ''plural''

# {{mathematics}} The [[coordinate]]s of a point measured as its [[Cartesian distance]] from the [[origin]] and the angle measured [[anticlockwise]]/[[counterclockwise]] from the [[x-axis|''x''-axis]] to a line joining the point to the origin.

